    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi dei eterni, anno ab incarnationis
                        eius millesimo centesimo quinquagesimo quinto, septimo idus ianuarii,
                        indictione quarta. Manifestus sum ego <persName ref="#people/3215"
                            >Passavanti</persName> quondam <persName ref="#people/3216"
                            >Sesmondini</persName> filius quia pro domini amore et anime mee
                        redemptione offero et inrevocabiliter trado omnipotenti deo et <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3206">sanctorum eius Iacobi et
                            Gilii</orgName> et aliorum ad utilitatem et commodum <rs
                            key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/3207">Altepascensis</placeName> unam integram petiam
                        de terra que videtur esse posita prope <rs key="#Castle">castellum</rs> quod
                        nuncupatur <placeName ref="#places/3210">Puteum</placeName>, in loco qui
                        dicitur Vignale Donicato. Et est tenens unum caput in <rs key="#Roads">via
                            pubblica</rs>, aliud in terra <persName>Uberti</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Iohannis</persName> et <persName>Geche</persName> filie
                        quondam <persName>Loctieri</persName>. Latus unum tenet in terra iamdicti
                        Uberti, aliud in terra similiter Geche suprascripte. <foreign>Pena</foreign>
                        in duplum (…) et insuper penam argenti optimi solidorum centum. Quia tali
                        ordine hanc cartulam offertionis scribere rogavi <persName key="#Notary"
                            >Henrigum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarium</rs> domni inperatoris. Actum in pede castri
                        Putensi, in domo et super fenestra <persName>Martinelli</persName>. Signa
                        manus suprascripti Passavanti, qui alacri animo hanc offertionis cartulam
                        scribere rogavit. Signa manus <persName>Ughiccione</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Benefatii</persName> atque <persName>Paltonieri</persName> et
                            <persName>Buiamonti</persName> atque <persName>Bonefatii</persName>
                        filiorum suprascripti Ughiccionis rogatorum <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs>.
                        (S) Ego Henrigus domni imperatoris <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellio</rs> rogatu
                        Passavanti peractis et perfectis complevi et dedi.</ab>
                </div>
